48d0071fba95","tid":762410,"uid":86898,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6351656c74c5c548759b6b20a675433d201bb209","tid":762410,"uid":189160,"like":2,"dislike":50,"score":-48,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"稅率得果17%<br />\nMPF得果5%<br />\n外國稅率閒閒地都30-50%<br />\n香港已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"拎歐洲比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />福利/生活/人種都唔同，淨係識拎數字打飛機<br />\n<br />\n講交稅，最鍾意同新加坡比，話晒老對手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用實際例子講，假設一個人年收入港紙30萬<br />\n<br />\n新加坡人<br />\n$60000去強積金(20%) =可以俾首期/供樓，保證2.5%利息=自己袋<br />\n交薪俸稅~$3000<br />\n總結自己袋~$297000<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n$15000去強積金(5%) =可以輸，死前買棺材=俾基金佬<br />\n交薪俸稅~$10000<br />\n總結自己袋~$275000<br />\n<br />\n比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacbfffea48477ff8751a69818a98c0dfddfaf10","tid":762410,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2592d5b6a22e6b584b0834654c6548d0071fba95","tid":762410,"uid":86898,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6351656c74c5c548759b6b20a675433d201bb209","tid":762410,"uid":189160,"like":2,"dislike":50,"score":-48,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"稅率得果17%<br />\nMPF得果5%<br />\n外國稅率閒閒地都30-50%<br />\n香港已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"拎歐洲比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />福利/生活/人種都唔同，淨係識拎數字打飛機<br />\n<br />\n講交稅，最鍾意同新加坡比，話晒老對手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用實際例子講，假設一個人年收入港紙30萬<br />\n<br />\n新加坡人<br />\n$60000去強積金(20%) =可以俾首期/供樓，保證2.5%利息=自己袋<br />\n交薪俸稅~$3000<br />\n總結自己袋~$297000<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n$15000去強積金(5%) =可以輸，死前買棺材=俾基金佬<br />\n交薪俸稅~$10000<br />\n總結自己袋~$275000<br />\n<br />\n比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270d8c0f9567f109711f91b783e531027eba8182","tid":762410,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7317dd378f47923afcd3780fb0bd1add5c4fdcbc","tid":762410,"uid":189160,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"c6d18dfc739dcaa61b121585eb333c2a14432fdc","tid":762410,"uid":96486,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d1230fc6ddf3946e9d57d5ffa8bc8c95e884a1fe","tid":762410,"uid":189160,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:14:15.000Z","msg":"From支那網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每年4月15日是美国人报税截止日，今年因为恰逢复活节周末，因此延长到4月18日。交税是民众应守的法律义务，由于美国的税法相当复杂，因此填写税表就成为许多人的&ldquo;负担&rdquo;，根据国税局（IRS）的统计，2016年美国人报税填表平均花费13个小时及210美元。对于美国人的税率我们有位读者有兴趣，问道：&ldquo;听说美国的个税蛮高的，是真的吗？&rdquo;这个问题看似简单，其实回答起来还颇费口舌。<br />\n<br />\n根据现有的税法规定，2016年美国的联邦个人收入所得税（个税）的税率最低是10%，最高是39.6%。从最高税率来看，在发达国家中美国是比较低的，以G7国家为例：个税最高的是法国，最低的是加拿大。以下是G7国家个税最高税率：<br />\n<br />\n法国：59.6%<br />\n德国：57%<br />\n日本：55.95%<br />\n英国：50%<br />\n澳大利亚：47%<br />\n美国：39.6%<br />\n意大利：35.54%<br />\n加拿大：33%"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"支那人就死番支那啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"From支那網就等於支那人？<br />\n傻仔出黎搞下笑下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講多個殘酷既事實你知<br />\n過左30年哩度都係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"佢自己都唔敢list自己出黎, 支那最高稅率係5成架<img src=\"/as